  Locus:
    Daily: August 11
  Source:
    Description: December 5, 1914
    Title: Letter to Marianne von Goldschmidt-Rothschild
Title: For the Sake of the Whole
---
Are there relations of the heart that embrace what is most cruel for the
sake of wholeness? For the world is only world when everything is included.
